 <sect1 id="sec.admin.docupdates.sle12_ga">
  <title>September XX, 2014 (Initial release of &productname; 12)</title>

  <variablelist>
   <varlistentry>
    <term>The Apache HTTP Server</term>
    <listitem>
     <itemizedlist>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        Removed references to mono and mod_mono as it was removed from the
        distribution (FATE#313504).
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        Updated the chapter to Apache version 2.4 (FATE#316067).
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        Removed deprecated directive <literal>NameVirtualHost</literal> and
        updated <xref linkend="sec.apache2.configuration.manually.vhost"/>
        accordingly.
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        Updated <literal>Order</literal>, <literal>Allow</literal>, and
        <literal>Deny</literal> directives with standard
        <literal>Require</literal>.
       </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
       <para>
        Removed virtual "Snake Oil" company from
        <xref
      linkend="sec.apache2.ssl"/>.
       </para>
      </listitem>
     </itemizedlist>
    </listitem>
